.\" termin.al-summary: Edit published content.
.TH EDIT 1 "" "termin.al" "termin.al Manual"
.ftr B R
.ftr I R
.ftr BI R
.SH NAME
edit \- Edit published content.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
edit <path>
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Names the future published-content editing entry point. The current public corpus remains read-only.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
$ edit notes/sample-note.md
.fi
.SH NOTES
The command currently returns a stable unavailable-feature diagnostic and does not modify content.
.SH SEE ALSO
help(1), man(1)
